data.description: Welcome to this comfortable 3-bedroom, 2-full bathroom upgraded energy efficient home. This house is perfect for first time buyers or for a small family. The living room is spacious to host company and flows into a galley type kitchen. The kitchen consists of upgraded stainless steel appliances; range, dishwasher and refrigerator. The dining room oversees the front yard and can be used as either a breakfast nook or family dining room. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering space and serenity. You'll also appreciate the walk-in closet, ensuring your wardrobe is always well-organized. Both bathrooms and kitchen/dining room consist of new luxury vinyl tile. Step out the back door into an enclosed porch that is perfect as a sun room where morning coffee can be enjoyed daily and where plants can be brought in from the bad weather to keep them safe. From the enclosed porch step out onto a beautiful back deck that covers the width of the home. This back deck is perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings and consists of two outdoor outlets and a light for night time gatherings and fan for those hot summer days. In the backyard is a sturdy wood shed that is perfect for additional storage which allows more space to be available in the garage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this relaxing house your forever home.
